text.paragraph:
The usual maintenance dose is in the range of 1.25 to 20 mg daily, which may be given as a single dose or in divided doses (see 

                              Dosage Interval
                           ). Dosage increases should be made in increments of no more than 2.5 mg at weekly intervals based upon the patient’s blood glucose response.

Appropriate precautions should be taken (see 

                              PRECAUTIONS
                           ).
